message: Sangram Singh is an Indian wrestler, actor, motivational speaker, philanthropist, health expert, and honorary doctor.[1]  Sangram Singh has a motivational story about how he became a World Wrestling Champion from a paralyzed boy to a motivational speaker, social worker, and actor.[2]  Sangram Singh works for children's education and child rights and also funds orphan girls for their betterment and bright future.[3]  He has done films and also reality shows like Survivor India and Nach Baliye.
